  "text": "Is there anything at all that we could do that we are not doing to— besides eliminating the contact— to increase the physical energy of the instrument? I am Ra. There is the possibility/probability that the whirling of the water with spine erect would alter, somewhat, the distortion towards what you call pain which this entity experiences in the dorsal region on a continuous level. This in turn could aid in the distortion towards increase of physical energy to some extent.",
